@Width 72


This is the AmigaGuide® file telnetd_device.guide, produced by Makeinfo-1.55 from 
the input file telnetd.texinfo.

This file documents @{b}telnetd.device@{ub}, a @{b}serial.device@{ub} look-a-like that
allows serial applications on the Amiga to accept telnet connections.

Copyright (C) 1993 by Christopher A. Wichura.
All rights reserved.


@Node Main "telnetd_device.guide"

@{b}telnetd.device@{ub}
**************

   @{b}telnetd.device@{ub} is a @{b}serial.device@{ub} look-a-like that allows Amiga
serial applications, such as BBS programs, to accept telnet connections.


